{"tid":1026004,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"嚟緊4月同兩老去台北 有咩啱玩","createTime":"2019-02-17T18:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T16:54:48.000Z","uid":161821,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bc48fc7fd0119fdef3f2cc35bc6180e48cc2a841","tid":1026004,"uid":161821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:23:27.000Z","msg":"俾返啲背景先<br />\n<br />\n兩老大概都係差唔多退休嘅年紀咁啦 兩個都係第一次去台北 諗住自由行玩5日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣啲文青打卡位同誠品我諗兩老都冇乜興趣 咁除咗大路啲嘅夜市啊九分啊天燈啊滷肉飯啊呢啲飲飲食食嘅嘢之外之外 有咩景點係啱兩老去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外 有冇啲咩旅遊書可以推薦 因為都想俾兩老自己睇下有咩地方想去但佢地又唔係好識自己上網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb308d73d1df751bbde50a343b7959403a5346e","tid":1026004,"uid":161821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:28:10.000Z","msg":"聽朝再推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9e5c8d05c4d38fd6d9f3bfa43e173bf1830f1a","tid":1026004,"uid":149566,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:29:38.000Z","msg":"上次去淡水搭船過八里<br />\n雖然冇咩睇 但個景幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b9e83b16f6879e8b875964d84965ca9ff805c7","tid":1026004,"uid":30708,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:31:50.000Z","msg":"同50歲以上人士去旅行<br />\n必定跟團<br />\n唔駛煩，有咩事就一齊屌個導遊領隊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4bdeea5db46f1d7e36dc7a74ed2f00c86e3ca7","tid":1026004,"uid":31205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T18:33:12.000Z","msg":"可以去動物園+貓空<br />\n都spend到一日嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de273c884f219fec92a1aaa4648bf5778d762dd4","tid":1026004,"uid":161821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df9e5c8d05c4d38fd6d9f3bfa43e173bf1830f1a","tid":10260